      "containerId": "shape-box-deploy",
      "text": "Deploy Pipeline\ndeploy-staging.yml\n\nChange detection\n(infra / frontend / services)\n\nDocker build ARM64\n\nECR push\n→ eu-central-1.amazonaws.com\n\nCDK diff + deploy\n\nECS rolling deploy\n→ health check\n→ bruno/e2e tests",
      "fontSize": 16.687161246612465,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "originalText": "Deploy Pipeline\ndeploy-staging.yml\n\nChange detection\n(infra / frontend / services)\n\nDocker build ARM64\n\nECR push\n→ eu-central-1.amazonaws.com\n\nCDK diff + deploy\n\nECS rolling deploy\n→ health check\n→ bruno/e2e tests",
